SUMMARY: Learn the Basics of Entrepreneurship in Canada
DESCRIPTION:Are you thinking about starting a business or growing an idea
 ? Join the Entrepreneur Mentoring Program 2026 with Martin Copeland\, a s
 uccessful entrepreneur with more than 40 years of international business 
 experience.\n\n\nIn this interactive online program\, delivered in Englis
 h\, you will gain practical insights into starting and running a business
  in North America. You will also have the opportunity to ask questions an
 d learn directly from an experienced mentor.\n\n\nWhether you are new to 
 entrepreneurship or looking to strengthen your business knowledge\, this 
 program is a great place to be.\n\n
